OL,3,CAintree Festival 2026: Race times,
OL,4,Ctravel and dress code
OL,6,FThe 178th Grand National takes place
OL,7,Fthis weekend, at the iconic Aintree
OL,8,Fracecourse.
OL,10,FOver 150,000 people are expected at
OL,11,Fthe festival, which lasts three days
OL,12,Ffrom Thursday 9 April - Saturday 11
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FIt is thought that around 250,000
OL,16,Fpints will be drunk over the three-day
OL,17,Ffestival, with millions of people
OL,18,Fwatching Saturday's race world-wide.
OL,20,FYou can watch the races on ITV1 and
OL,21,FITVX from 1.30pm everyday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
