OL,3,CAintree Festival 2026: Race times,
OL,4,Ctravel and dress code
OL,6,FWhen does the racecourse open?
OL,8,FRacegoers are urged to leave plenty of
OL,9,Ftime and plan ahead when travelling to
OL,10,FAintree Racecourse.
OL,12,FThursday: Gates open at 11am
OL,14,FFriday: Gates open at 10.30am
OL,16,FSaturday: Gates open at 10am
OL,18,FRaces will start at 1.45pm on Thursday
OL,19,Fand Friday, and 12.45pm on Saturday,
OL,20,Fwith the iconic Grand National race to
OL,21,Fstart at 4pm on Saturday 11 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
