OL,3,CAintree Festival 2026: Race times,
OL,4,Ctravel and dress code
OL,6,FTravelling by bus?
OL,8,FStagecoach Manchester and Merseyside
OL,9,Fwill be running a dedicated shuttle
OL,10,Fbus service from Liverpool city centre
OL,11,Fto Aintree Racecourse across all three
OL,12,Fdays of the festival.
OL,14,FPassengers can board the shuttle from
OL,15,FElliot Street in the city centre for a
OL,16,Fdirect journey to Park Lane (Aintree
OL,17,FStation), located just a short walk
OL,18,Ffrom the racecourse entrance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
