OL,3,CAintree Festival 2026: Race times,
OL,4,Ctravel and dress code
OL,6,FThe 300, 310 and 345 services run
OL,7,Fregularly between Queen Square bus
OL,8,Fstation and the Aintree area, but
OL,9,Fthese services will be on a diversion
OL,10,Fand may not stop at their usual stops.
OL,12,FTickets are priced at #5 for an adult
OL,13,Fsingle and #6 for an adult return.
OL,15,FTravelling by rail?
OL,17,FMerseyrail will run services between
OL,18,FLiverpool city centre and Aintree
OL,19,Fstations on the Northern line every
OL,20,Fseven-and-a-half minutes before and
OL,21,Fafter the races.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
