OL,3,CAintree Festival 2026: Race times,
OL,4,Ctravel and dress code
OL,6,FThe increased service will run from
OL,7,F10am - 1pm (before the races) and
OL,8,F4.30pm - 8pm (after the races).
OL,10,FPassengers can now use the new Tap &
OL,11,FGo smart ticketing system across the
OL,12,FMerseyrail network, but they are
OL,13,Fadvised to buy tickets in advance if
OL,14,Fpossible.
OL,16,FTravelling by car?
OL,18,FDuring the races driving around the
OL,19,Fracecourse will be severely limited,
OL,20,Fand a "no waiting" area will be in
OL,21,Fplace.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
