OL,3,CAintree Festival 2026: Race times,
OL,4,Ctravel and dress code
OL,6,FFriday 10 April is Ladies' Day - one
OL,7,Fof the biggest fashion days of the
OL,8,Fyear - so you can expect to see
OL,9,Fextravagant outfits, big hats and
OL,10,Fbright colours.
OL,12,FHowever there is no official style
OL,13,Fguide for the Aintree Grand National,
OL,14,Fand racegoers have no obligation to
OL,15,Fdress up, but sportswear, team colours/
OL,16,Fkits and fancy dress are not permitted.
OL,18,FLadies' Day will also see the Style
OL,19,FAwards, where the two two best dressed
OL,20,Fracegoers will be crowned, along with
OL,21,Fthe most sustainably dressed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
